{"tid":2280850,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"如何消滅神蹟？","createTime":"2020-11-10T21:09:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T22:18:35.000Z","uid":47901,"like":2,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"249806684e74e244f42b555964b27ba0038a299b","tid":2280850,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T21:09:58.000Z","msg":"曾經科學界有理論：質量守恆<br />\n<br />\n但後來發現質量竟然不一定守恆，例如核聚變或者裂變<br />\n<br />\n最後當然是修改科學理論<br />\n<br />\n否則核聚變或裂變就是神蹟了<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;神蹟&rdquo;會不斷發生，所以科學理論要不斷修改，那麼神蹟就會消失<br />\n<br />\n雖然質量守恆破功，但因為質量是能量的其中一種形式（E=mc^2），即係無中生有或有中消失的質量可以用能量守恆去解釋，所以即使質量不守恆的現象出現了，也未致於有神蹟發生的餘地<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n或者將來會有無中生有或有中消失的能量，即是能量不守恆的現象出現<br />\n<br />\n？？？？= E?????<br />\n<br />\n當然新神蹟永遠有機會俾新的物理公式去消滅<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，<br />\n<br />\n地平撚的背後用意，唔係玩膠咁簡單，他們在考驗我地對科學論說的&ldquo;信心&rdquo;，若有人要提出某d科學論證是基於地圓說，唯有自己圍地球行個圈先，或上太空站望返落地球去prove左先，否則該人大量的繼後科學推論還是建基於&ldquo;信心&rdquo;，&ldquo;faith&rdquo; （to the god of science)"},{"pid":"8d9aa0eab668359b81b477a6d51e8a72f89c7a81","tid":2280850,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-10T21:36:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lbzF0JktG2g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlbzF0JktG2g&d=dtUYnMymWvCkGCbOKSm7ImWjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=48365bfa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lbzF0JktG2g</a>"},{"pid":"5ff6d305fa0eaec77b6c9f99c06a3144ed69c435","tid":2280850,"uid":320858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T00:40:47.000Z","msg":"你信咩"},{"pid":"4024f1e52c3865b1da11b39779968446f04e85a2","tid":2280850,"uid":112845,"like":12,"dislike":7,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T01:30:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7cf0ea01831b2647a52b91beb26b74095096e9e","tid":2280850,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T06:11:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agre